snippet.title: Garbage Crew! Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592720?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=direct
Join the Garbage Crew! Discord community: https://discord.gg/5meE9AryFc
Follow Garbage Crew! on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/garbagecrewgame
Follow Garbage Crew! on X: https://twitter.com/GarbageCrewGame
Follow the development: https://mastodon.gamedev.place/@xeetsh

Garbage Crew! is a chaotic, roguelike, couch coop game for up to four players. Work in a team to empty garbage cans, extinguish fires clean up the city and... fight?! All while keeping up with the garbage truck whose driver really hates to stop!
